egin="00:25.796" end="00:25.995">な</span><span begin="00:25.995" end="00:26.337">た</span><span begin="00:26.337" end="00:26.824">へ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">致生活在不曾相见的明天的你</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ma da mi na i a shi ta wo i ki ru a na ta e</span></p><p begin="00:27.649" end="00:32.017" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:27.649" end="00:27.963">引</span><span begin="00:27.963" end="00:28.158">き</span><span begin="00:28.158" end="00:28.432">出</span><span begin="00:28.432" end="00:28.661">し</span><span begin="00:28.661" end="00:29.051">の</span><span begin="00:29.482" end="00:29.827">奥</span><span begin="00:29.827" end="00:29.992">に</span><span begin="00:29.992" end="00:30.321">預</span><span begin="00:30.321" end="00:30.651">け</span><span begin="00:30.651" end="00:30.817">た</span><span begin="00:30.817" end="00:31.179">こ</span><span begin="00:31.179" end="00:31.328">の</span><span begin="00:31.328" end="00:31.491">手</span><span begin="00:31.491" end="00:32.017">紙</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">寄放在抽屉深处的这信笺</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">hi ki da shi no o ku ni a zu ke ta ko no te ga mi</span></p><p begin="00:33.000" end="00:37.597" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:33.000" end="00:33.342">い</span><span begin="00:33.342" end="00:33.496">つ</span><span begin="00:33.496" end="00:33.794">の</span><span begin="00:33.794" end="00:34.007">日</span><span begin="00:34.007" end="00:34.397">か</span> <span begin="00:34.849" end="00:35.008">時</span><span begin="00:35.008" end="00:35.340">間</span><span begin="00:35.340" end="00:35.650">を</span><span begin="00:35.650" end="00:36.005">飛</span><span begin="00:36.005" end="00:36.158">び</span><span begin="00:36.158" end="00:36.665">越</span><span begin="00:36.665" end="00:36.990">え</span><span begin="00:36.990" end="00:37.597">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">希望有一天 能跨越时间</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">i tsu no hi ka ji ka n wo to bi ko e te</span></p><p begin="00:37.973" end="00:42.814" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:37.973" end="00:38.146">そ</span><span begin="00:38.146" end="00:38.315">の</span><span begin="00:38.315" end="00:38.662">背</span><span begin="00:38.662" end="00:39.323">中</span><span begin="00:39.323" end="00:39.622">を</span><span begin="00:39.622" end="00:40.014">そ</span><span begin="00:40.014" end="00:40.167">っ</span><span begin="00:40.167" end="00:40.422">と</span> <span begin="00:40.649" end="00:40.961">押</span><span begin="00:40.961" end="00:41.315">せ</span><span begin="00:41.315" end="00:41.466">た</span><span begin="00:41.466" end="00:41.997">ら</span><span begin="00:41.997" end="00:42.089">い</span><span begin="00:42.089" end="00:42.189">い</span><span begin="00:42.189" end="00:42.814">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在你背后轻推一把就好了</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so no se na ka wo so tto o se ta ra i i na</span></p><p begin="00:43.636" end="00:53.686" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:43.636" end="00:45.000">難</span><span begin="00:45.000" end="00:45.210">し</span><span begin="00:45.210" end="00:45.486">い</span><span begin="00:45.486" end="00:45.948">ね</span> <span begin="00:46.329" end="00:47.332">報</span><span begin="00:47.332" end="00:47.678">わ</span><span begin="00:47.678" end="00:48.026">れ</span><span begin="00:48.026" end="00:48.339">る</span><span begin="00:48.339" end="00:48.665">と</span><span begin="00:48.665" end="00:49.004">は</span><span begin="00:49.004" end="00:49.992">限</span><span begin="00:49.992" end="00:50.336">ら</span><span begin="00:50.336" end="00:50.524">な</span><span begin="00:50.524" end="00:50.726">い</span> <span begin="00:51.009" end="00:52.665">現</span><span begin="00:52.665" end="00:53.686">実</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有些艰难啊 所谓回报未必现实</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">mu zu ka shi i ne mu ku wa re ru to wa ka gi ra na i ge n ji tsu</span></p><p begin="00:54.252" end="00:56.108" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:54.252" end="00:54.847">そっ</span><span begin="00:54.847" end="00:55.326">ち</span><span begin="00:55.326" end="00:55.677">は</span><span begin="00:55.677" end="00:55.898">ど</span><span begin="00:55.898" end="00:56.108">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你现在过得如何呢</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so tchi wa do u</span></p><p begin="00:56.819" end="01:03.624" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:56.819" end="00:56.974">理</span><span begin="00:56.974" end="00:57.476">想</span><span begin="00:57.476" end="00:57.900">像</span><span begin="00:57.995" end="00:58.321">に</span><span begin="00:58.321" end="00:58.808">苦</span><span begin="00:58.808" end="00:59.324">し</span><span begin="00:59.324" end="00:59.623">ん</span><span begin="00:59.623" end="01:00.954">で</span><span begin="01:01.301" end="01:01.667">な</span><span begin="01:01.667" end="01:01.983">い</span><span begin="01:01.983" end="01:02.360">か</span><span begin="01:02.360" end="01:03.624">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有没有因理想而痛苦着呢</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ri so u zo u ni ku ru shi n de na i ka na</span></p><p begin="01:04.342" end="01:09.349" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="01:04.342" end="01:04.691">あ</span><span begin="01:04.691" end="01:05.008">な</span><span begin="01:05.008" end="01:05.480">た</span><span begin="01:05.480" end="01:06.012">は</span><span begin="01:06.012" end="01:06.734">今</span> <span begin="01:07.008" end="01:07.669">笑</span><span begin="01:07.669" end="01:08.000">え</span><span begin="01:08.000" end="01:08.153">て</span><span begin="01:08.153" end="01:08.623">ま</span><span begin="01:08.623" end="01:08.981">す</span><span begin="01:08.981" end="01:09.349">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如今的你 绽放笑容了吗</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">a na ta wa i ma wa ra e te ma su ka</span></p><p begin="01:09.696" end="01:14.727" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="01:09.696" end="01:10.635">私</span><span begin="01:10.635" end="01:10.849">に</span><span begin="01:10.849" end="01:11.664">嘘</span><span begin="01:11.664" end="01:12.074">は</span><span begin="01:12.357" end="01:12.657">つ</span><span begin="01:12.657" end="01:12.997">か</span><span begin="01:12.997" end="01:13.658">な</span><span begin="01:13.658" end="01:13.933">い</span><span begin="01:14.009" end="01:14.338">で</span><span begin="01:14.338" end="01:14.727">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">还请不要对我说谎哦</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">wa ta shi ni u so wa tsu ka na i de yo</span></p><p begin="01:14.998" end="01:19.172" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:14.998" end="01:15.306">泣</span><span begin="01:15.306" end="01:15.637">き</span><span begin="01:15.637" end="01:15.962">た</span><span begin="01:15.962" end="01:16.171">い</span><span begin="01:16.171" end="01:16.988">時</span><span begin="01:16.988" end="01:17.376">に</span> <span begin="01:17.660" end="01:17.997">こ</span><span begin="01:17.997" end="01:18.305">ぼ</span><span begin="01:18.305" end="01:18.667">す</span><span begin="01:18.667" end="01:18.859">の</span><span begin="01:18.859" end="01:19.172">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为啊 想哭的时候流下的</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">na ki ta i to ki ni ko bo su no wa</span></p><p begin="01:19.259" end="01:25.607" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:19.259" end="01:19.349">「</span><span begin="01:19.349" end="01:19.976">大</span><span begin="01:19.976" end="01:20.662">丈</span><span begin="01:20.662" end="01:20.924">夫</span><span begin="01:20.924" end="01:20.998">」</span><span begin="01:20.998" end="01:21.345">じゃ</span><span begin="01:21.345" end="01:21.520">な</span><span begin="01:21.520" end="01:22.585">い</span> <span begin="01:23.338" end="01:24.008">涙</span><span begin="01:24.008" end="01:24.150">だ</span><span begin="01:24.150" end="01:24.669">か</span><span begin="01:24.669" end="01:24.966">ら</span><span begin="01:24.966" end="01:25.607">ね</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不是「没关系」 而是眼泪不是吗</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">"da i jo u bu" ja na i na mi da da ka ra ne</span></p><p begin="01:36.988" end="01:41.291" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:36.988" end="01:37.343">完</span><span begin="01:37.343" end="01:37.794">璧</span><span begin="01:37.794" end="01:37.997">主</span><span begin="01:37.997" end="01:38.427">義</span> <span begin="01:38.829" end="01:39.139">突</span><span begin="01:39.139" end="01:39.613">然</span> <span begin="01:39.613" end="01:39.916">発</span><span begin="01:39.916" end="01:40.451">症</span><span begin="01:40.451" end="01:40.657">さ</span><span begin="01:40.657" end="01:40.994">せ</span><span begin="01:40.994" end="01:41.291">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">完美主义突然发作</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ka n pe ki shu gi to tsu ze n ha ssho u sa se te</span></p><p begin="01:42.125" end="01:46.727" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:42.125" end="01:42.646">全</span><span begin="01:42.646" end="01:42.813">て</span><span begin="01:42.813" end="01:43.147">が</span><span begin="01:43.147" end="01:43.495">嫌</span><span begin="01:43.495" end="01:43.654">に</span><span begin="01:43.654" end="01:43.976">な</span><span begin="01:43.976" end="01:44.346">る</span><span begin="01:44.489" end="01:44.836">事</span><span begin="01:44.836" end="01:45.002">も</span><span begin="01:45.002" end="01:45.328">た</span><span begin="01:45.328" end="01:45.504">ま</span><span begin="01:45.504" end="01:45.977">に</span><span begin="01:45.977" end="01:46.331">あ</span><span begin="01:46.331" end="01:46.727">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">偶尔也会厌弃着一切</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">su be te ga i ya ni na ru ko to mo ta ma ni a ru</span></p><p begin="01:47.472" end="01:51.751" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:47.472" end="01:47.686">こ</span><span begin="01:47.686" end="01:47.968">の</span><span begin="01:47.968" end="01:48.467">気</span><span begin="01:48.467" end="01:48.643">質</span><span begin="01:48.643" end="01:49.038">は</span> <span begin="01:49.474" end="01:49.833">相</span><span begin="01:49.833" end="01:50.010">変</span><span begin="01:50.010" end="01:50.151">わ</span><span begin="01:50.151" end="01:50.328">ら</span><span begin="01:50.328" end="01:50.714">ず</span><span begin="01:50.812" end="01:51.197">か</span><span begin="01:51.310" end="01:51.751">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这种气质还是老样子吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ko no ki shi tsu wa a i ka wa ra zu ka na</span></p><p begin="01:52.675" end="01:57.173" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:52.675" end="01:52.968">優</span><span begin="01:52.968" end="01:53.485">し</span><span begin="01:53.485" end="01:53.739">く</span><span begin="01:53.880" end="01:54.019">な</span><span begin="01:54.019" end="01:54.172">れ</span><span begin="01:54.172" end="01:54.368">な</span><span begin="01:54.368" end="01:54.670">い</span><span begin="01:54.670" end="01:54.824">ね</span><span begin="01:54.824" end="01:55.145">い</span><span begin="01:55.145" end="01:55.305">つ</span><span begin="01:55.305" end="01:55.651">も</span> <span begin="01:55.651" end="01:55.989">自</span><span begin="01:55.989" end="01:56.504">分</span><span begin="01:56.504" end="01:56.661">に</span><span begin="01:56.661" end="01:57.173">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">总是没法温柔地对自己呢</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ya sa shi ku na re na i ne i tsu mo ji bu n ni wa</span></p><p begin="01:58.345" end="02:08.233" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:58.345" end="01:59.323">前</span><span begin="01:59.323" end="01:59.670">を</span><span begin="01:59.670" end="01:59.993">向</span><span begin="01:59.993" end="02:00.141">い</span><span begin="02:00.141" end="02:00.631">て</span> <span begin="02:01.003" end="02:01.985">歩</span><span begin="02:01.985" end="02:02.320">く</span><span begin="02:02.320" end="02:02.662">こ</span><span begin="02:02.662" end="02:03.010">と</span><span begin="02:03.010" end="02:03.318">だ</span><span begin="02:03.318" end="02:03.656">け</span><span begin="02:03.656" end="02:04.170">が</span> <span begin="02:04.170" end="02:04.941">強</span><span begin="02:04.941" end="02:05.481">さ</span><span begin="02:05.481" end="02:05.772">じゃ</span><span begin="02:06.003" end="02:06.305">な</span><span begin="02:06.305" end="02:07.097">い</span><span begin="02:07.097" end="02:07.321">ん</span><span begin="02:07.321" end="02:07.643">だ</span><span begin="02:07.643" end="02:08.233">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不是一味向前走才叫做坚强</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ma e wo mu i te a ru ku ko to da ke ga tsu yo sa ja na i n da yo</span></p><p begin="02:08.979" end="02:10.961" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="02:08.979" end="02:09.994">後</span><span begin="02:09.994" end="02:10.323">ろ</span><span begin="02:10.323" end="02:10.961">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">若不回头</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">u shi ro wo</span></p><p begin="02:11.499" end="02:18.321" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="02:11.499" end="02:11.663">向</span><span begin="02:11.663" end="02:12.008">か</span><span begin="02:12.008" end="02:12.147">な</span><span begin="02:12.147" end="02:12.509">きゃ</span> <span begin="02:12.859" end="02:13.007">見</span><span begin="02:13.007" end="02:13.340">え</span><span begin="02:13.340" end="02:13.487">な</span><span begin="02:13.487" end="02:13.956">い</span><span begin="02:13.956" end="02:14.310">そ</span><span begin="02:14.310" end="02:15.437">の</span><span begin="02:16.001" end="02:16.649">足</span><span begin="02:16.649" end="02:18.321">跡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">怎能看到来时的足迹</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">mu ka na kya mi e na i so no a shi a to</span></p><p begin="02:19.010" end="02:24.009" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="02:19.010" end="02:19.348">あ</span><span begin="02:19.348" end="02:19.657">な</span><span begin="02:19.657" end="02:20.168">た</span><span begin="02:20.168" end="02:20.649">は</span><span begin="02:20.649" end="02:21.356">今</span> <span begin="02:21.678" end="02:22.002">ど</span><span begin="02:22.002" end="02:22.330">こ</span><span begin="02:22.330" end="02:22.666">に</span><span begin="02:22.666" end="02:22.827">い</span><span begin="02:22.827" end="02:23.280">ま</span><span begin="02:23.280" end="02:23.659">す</span><span begin="02:23.659" end="02:24.009">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如今的你 又会在哪里呢</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">a na ta wa i ma do ko ni i ma su ka</span></p><p begin="02:24.350" end="02:29.405" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="02:24.350" end="02:24.997">迷</span><span begin="02:24.997" end="02:25.316">う</span><span begin="02:25.316" end="02:25.503">た</span><span begin="02:25.503" end="02:26.010">び</span><span begin="02:26.010" end="02:26.175">に</span><span begin="02:26.175" end="02:26.661">思</span><span begin="02:26.661" end="02:26.845">い</span><span begin="02:26.845" end="02:27.276">出</span><span begin="02:27.276" end="02:27.680">し</span><span begin="02:27.680" end="02:28.672">て</span><span begin="02:28.672" end="02:28.950">ほ</span><span begin="02:28.950" end="02:29.188">し</span><span begin="02:29.188" end="02:29.405">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">希望每当迷茫的时候你都能回想起</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ma yo u ta bi ni o mo i da shi te ho shi i</span></p><p begin="02:29.680" end="02:36.910" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="02:29.680" end="02:30.681">大人</span><span begin="02:30.681" end="02:30.847">に</span><span begin="02:30.847" end="02:31.178">な</span><span begin="02:31.178" end="02:31.324">る</span><span begin="02:31.324" end="02:31.641">と</span><span begin="02:31.641" end="02:32.042">は</span> <span begin="02:32.341" end="02:32.989">何</span><span begin="02:32.989" end="02:33.308">か</span><span begin="02:33.308" end="02:33.496">捨</span><span begin="02:33.496" end="02:33.838">て</span